songs.full_title: Ascribe Greatness by Don Moen
songs.title: Ascribe Greatness

description.plain:
The words of this song are from a song Moses sang (with Joshua) in Deuteronomy 32. The lyrics are from verse 3 and 4, though Moses' song is in verse 1 through 43.

Deuteronomy 32:3-4
3 Because I will publish the name of the LORD: ascribe ye greatness unto our God.
4 He is the Rock, his work is perfect: for all his ways are judgment: a God of truth and without iniquity, just and right is he.

Moses' song is a song concerning salvation, found only in God, teaching full trust in God, the Rock, who is faithful and without injustice, and whose work is perfect.
